<h3>Viva Voce Schedule</h3>
<p>The Royal Civil Service Commission would like to announce the Schedule and Venue for BCSE 2017 Viva Voce as follows: </p>
<b>Schedule: October 16 – 24, 2017</b></br></br>

<b>Reporting Time:</b></br>
Morning: 8.50 AM</br>
Afternoon: 1.30 PM</br></br>

<b>Venues:</b></br>
<ul>
<li>PGDPA Category: RCSC Secretariat (Near Tashichhodzong)</li>
<li>PGDFM Category: RCSC Secretariat (Near Tashichhodzong)</li>
<li>PGDE & Dzongkha Category: Lungtenzampa Middle Secondary School</li>
<li>Technical Category – Bio Science Group: Lungtenzampa Middle Secondary School</li>
<li>Technical Category – Medical Group incl. Traditional Medicine: Lungtenzampa Middle Secondary School</li> 
<li>Technical Category – Civil Engineering Group: RIM, Semtokha</li>
<li>Technical Category – Engg. other than Civil Engg.: RIM, Semtokha</li>
<li>Technical Category – ICT, Law & Statistics Group: RIM, Semtokha</li>
</ul>


