<b>Requirements for Viva Voce</b></br>
<ul><b>
	<li>Candidates must come in formal dress, including Kabney and Rachu.</li>
	<li>Candidates must report on time.</li>
	<li>Candidates shall be allowed to appear for Viva Voce only upon production of e-Admit card. </li>
	<li>Candidates are required to produce Certificate of Merit (if any) in original during the time of Viva Voce.</li>
</b></ul>
<b>Note: </b>

<p><i>RCSC would like to take this opportunity to remind candidates who were given deadline extension till October 23, 2017 to produce the original Degree Transcripts to remember the deadline and submit the documents accordingly.</i></p>

