<p>The Royal Civil Service Commission would like to announce the following details regarding the Preliminary Examination of the Bhutan Civil Service Examination 2017:</p>
<ol>
	<li> 	<b>Schedule</b>:
 		<ul>
    	<li><b>Date </b>: August 06, 2017 (Sunday)</li>
 		<li><b>Reporting Time </b>: 9.00 AM</li>
 		<li><b>Examination Start Time</b> : 9.30 AM </li>
 		<li><b>Examination Venue</b> :<a href="http://www.rcsc.gov.bt/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Examination-Venue.pdf"> Click Here</a></li>
        </ul>
	</li>

	<li><b>Conduct of candidate </b>: <a href="http://www.rcsc.gov.bt/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Conduct-of-Candidates.pdf">Click Here</a></li>
	<li><b>e-Registration Statistics :<a href="http://www.rcsc.gov.bt/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/PE-Statistics.pdf"> Click Here</a></b></li>
	<li><b>Materials required for the Preliminary Examination:</b>
